{"lemma":"اِسْتِعاناتُ","slug":"اِسْتِعاناتُ","root":"ع.#.ن","root_slug":"ع-_-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-_-ن","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n31106"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A7%D9%90%D8%B3%D9%92%D8%AA%D9%90%D8%B9%D8%A7%D9%86%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of اِسْتَعَانَ (istaʕāna) (form X)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"asking for help or assistance"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Verbal noun of اِسْتَعَانَ (istaʕāna)."},"ipa":["/is.ti.ʕaː.na/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n31106","headword_ar":"استعانهُ","root":"Ewn","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sought, desired, demanded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"begged, of him, aid, help,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"assistance."},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AisotaEanotuhu","text_ar":"اِسْتَعَنْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AisotaEanotu bihi","text_ar":"اِسْتَعَنْتُ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb,) or both, (K,) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA^aEaAnaniY","text_ar":"فَاَعَانَنِى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, * K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAwananiY","text_ar":"عَاوَنَنِى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, TA,) for which last, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaw~ananiY","text_ar":"عَوَّنَنِى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is erroneously put in the copies of the K; (TA;) [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I sought,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of him, aid, &c., and he aided me."},{"kind":"text","text":"] The alteration of the infirm letter ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A","text_ar":"ا"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is made in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstEAn","text_ar":"استعان"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AEAn","text_ar":"اعان","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"in imitation of a general rule [which requires it when that alteration is made in the unaugmented triliteral verb], though"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAna","text_ar":"عَانَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaEuwnu","text_ar":"يَعُونُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [as their source of derivation,] is not used. (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"b","text_ar":"ب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bi","text_ar":"بِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Harofu A@sotiEaAnapK","text_ar":"حَرْفُ ا@سْتِعَانَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A particle denotative of seeking aid,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,] because when you say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Darabotu biAls~ayofi","text_ar":"ضَرَبْتُ بِالسَّيْفِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"katabotu biAlqalami","text_ar":"كَتَبْتُ بِالقَلَمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"barayotu biAlmudoyapi","text_ar":"بَرَيْتُ بِالمُدْيَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", it is as though you said"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AisotaEanotu","text_ar":"اِسْتَعَنْتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bih`*ihi AlA^adawaAti Ealay h`*ihi AlA^afoEaAli","text_ar":"بِهٰذِهِ الاَدَوَاتِ عَلَي هٰذِهِ الاَفْعَالِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I sought aid of these instruments,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made use of them as means, against,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to perform, these actions of smiting"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (TA.) [And you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstEAn","text_ar":"استعان"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"binafosihi","text_ar":"بِنَفْسِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sought self-help,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exerted himself,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiy A^amorK","text_ar":"فِي اَمْرٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in an affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohi","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"against it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"him."},{"kind":"text","text":"]       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstEAn","text_ar":"استعان"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He shaved his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAnap","text_ar":"عَانَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pubes;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEay~ana","text_ar":"تَعَيَّنَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEaw~ana","text_ar":"تَعَوَّنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", on the authority of ISd. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Mgh","S","Msb","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}